Lynn Borden https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lynn_Borden 0 Lynn Borden (March 24, 1937 – March 3, 2015) was an American actress, possibly best known for her role as "Barbara Baxter" in the final season of the Shirley Booth sitcom Hazel on CBS (1965-66).
